features.name: Ashelor to Vinland Bypass
features.notes: Getting to Vinland from Ashelor is as easy as "/dest Vinland", whereas to get to Ashelor from Vinland, you must "/dest Terestai" and then "/dest Ashelor" once you are on the purple line.

features.name: Ashelor to Shen Link
features.notes: You must have your destination set to "Ashelor" to arrive in Ashelor. Departing from Ashelor, set your destination to "Entrana" to head east, otherwise you will automatically head west.

features.name: Ashelor to Adina Link
features.notes: You must have your destination set to "Ashelor" to arrive in Ashelor. Departing from Ashelor, set your destination to "Bloom" to head north, otherwise you will automatically head south.
